{"tid":475020,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)明日之後 人造天劫","createTime":"2017-11-20T17:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T19:59:36.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6dda954ab23e48ae785ea8d631a7dc0f614e1498","tid":475020,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T17:05:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=0EbMQFfxnXs2umNvcwVZvW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f7791e8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=0EbMQFfxnXs2umNvcwVZvW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=61465312\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/58/The_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F58%2FThe_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg&h=bc58c67a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f5/Geostorm_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff5%2FGeostorm_Poster.jpg&h=f79748bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在一片已經極度融化的南極冰川上，古氣候學家傑克&middot;霍爾與同事弗蘭克和傑森在冰川上考察時，親眼目睹整個拉森冰架全部斷裂。傑克隨後將有關全球暖化調查結果，在新德里舉行的聯合國研討會上作出報告，聲明兩極冰川融化已經阻斷了北大西洋洋流的暖洋流，而這種情況繼續持續下去將會在未來形成另一個冰河時期。但參加會議的各國元首對此感到荒謬，美國副總統雷蒙&middot;貝克甚至把傑克的理論當作笑話看待..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述當地球上的天候已呈現失控狀態時，人類能依靠天候控制衛星來控制天候。但某日，該衛星竟因未知原因而發生故障，使得地球上的天候發生暴走，各種毀滅性的天災降臨城市、造成嚴重災害。此時，唯一能阻止這一切的是一對兄弟衛星工程師，他們在行動的同時也意外發現到一項刺殺美國總統的陰謀正在醞釀<br />\n<br />\n1 20AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=0EbMQFfxnXs2umNvcwVZvW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=12a85387\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=0EbMQFfxnXs2umNvcwVZvW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a491293a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a38991f6d75e0ef886bc10fd4b03b4ef28574e","tid":475020,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T17:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e42ba2c3dde60e22ad654d67cc0ec73280ff05f","tid":475020,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579d5626c8778c7d67bf48cf87030365eaa643cc","tid":475020,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3e74b5cb0fdc2a099c69ea738541d3f23c076e","tid":475020,"uid":29160,"like":0,"